title: From Bronze to Plat! How to Climb Tricks and Tips :)

embed.description: From Bronze to Plat! How to Climb Tricks and Tips :)

body:
Hey guys and girls :)
Today i am starting a special series on my stream as I am going to climb from Bronze to atleast Plat.
If u wanna get some tips and tricks on how to climb :) and how to get out of elo hell then come and join me.
Ofc if u just wanna chat with other viewers and me u are most welcome aswell :p
Feel free to ask for Tips or that I play a specific champion even tho atm my championpool is limited.
So we are mostly gonna play the new Akali and good old Zed.
I hope I see u guys soon! Really appreciate everyone joining and dont be shy :p

greetings onidemoni
